{"tid":238312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星島日報：中央頗滿意陳茂波　不應因政治考慮換人","createTime":"2017-05-11T02:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T03:56:09.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d726f3902b4d489429cd616e1278d3e52f8a0ca","tid":238312,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:55:43.000Z","msg":"自曾俊華辭任財政司司長參選特首後，特首梁振英將發展局局長陳茂波升格做財爺，但任期僅4個月的他，甫上任就鬧出豪裝官邸風波。《星島日報》政情專欄《大棋盤》報道，候任特首林鄭月娥一直打算另覓財爺人選，但「聞說中央官員頗滿意」陳茂波的表現，又指林鄭「不應因為政治考慮而要『犧牲』他。"},{"pid":"c18e35ea0aac5931eec4d0c19bbe15682e26162c","tid":238312,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56678835&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56678835%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170511&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6ce84f29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56678835%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170511&h=14285c08\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56678835&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170511</a>"},{"pid":"06c5a8e78513192b178c9d089ac8bfdda128760d","tid":238312,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36aacfffe6d1ebdd450ac38aa508eb916ca6a89c","tid":238312,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8f2aab9ed3052ef76c1a4964d14cb8d455101b","